{"product_id":"hej-organic-naked-remove-it-all-micellar-cleansing-water-150ml","title":"HEJ Organic Naked Remove It All Micellar Cleansing Water 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaked is a fragrance-free skincare line with highly effective and 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMicellar Cleansing Water's micelles penetrate deep into your pores. With the help of algae complex and zinc, it can effectively help reduce sebum production and the development of skin impurities. At the same time, hyaluronic acid gives you a long-lasting boost of freshness!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCleans deep into the pores and moisturizes \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eContains zinc to reduce sebum production and impurities\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith hyaluronic acid for long-lasting moisture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eParticularly suitable for impure, oily and combination skin  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance-free and natural  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply morning and evening to a cotton pad and gently rub it over your face, eyes and lips. If you have heavier make-up, place the pad briefly on the relevant area of ​​skin and let it take effect. You don't have to wash it off! Also suitable for contact lens wearers. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Glycerin, Betaine, Coco-Glucoside, Zinc Pca, Sodium Hyaluronate, Prunus Armeniaca Fruit Extract*, Fucus Spiralis Extract, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Extract*, Tetraselmis Chui Extract, Levulinic Acid, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Levulinate, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Sodium Hydroxide \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905775046983,"sku":null,"price":9.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-naked-remove-it-all-micellar-cleansing-water-150ml-797159.png?v=1739897168","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hej-organic-naked-remove-it-all-micellar-cleansing-water-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}